st Seneca]] || 1995-1998 || Joined [[OJHL|OPJHL]]\n|- align=\"center\"\n| '''[[North York Rangers]] (I)''' || [[North York]] || 1967-1972 || Joined [[Ontario Provincial Junior A Hockey League (1972-1987)|OPJHL]]\n|- align=\"center\"\n| '''[[North York Rangers]] (II)''' || [[North York]] || 1992-1998 || Joined [[OJHL|OPJHL]]\n|- align=\"center\"\n| '''[[Oshawa Legionaires]]''' || [[Oshawa]] || 1972-1998 || Joined [[OJHL|OPJHL]]\n|- align=\"center\"\n| '''[[Peterborough Stars|Peterborough Lions]]''' || [[Peterborough, Ontario|Peterborough]] || 1972-1989  || Joined [[OJHL|CJBHL]]\n|- align=\"center\"\n| '''[[Pickering Panthers]]''' || [[Pickering, Ontario|Pickering]] || 1972-1998 || Joined [[OJHL|OPJHL]]\n|- align=\"center\"\n| '''[[Pittsburgh Jr. Penguins]]''' || [[Pittsburgh]] || 1997-1998 || Joined [[Empire Junior B Hockey League|EmpJHL]]\n|- align=\"center\"\n| '''[[Port Credit Titans]]''' || [[Port Credit, Ontario|Port Credit]] || 1979-1987 || Folded\n|- align=\"center\"\n| '''[[Port Hope Buzzards]]''' || [[Port Hope, Ontario|Port Hope]] || 1996-1998 || Joined [[OJHL|OPJHL]]\n|- align=\"center\"\n| '''[[Quinte Hawks]]''' || [[Deseronto]] || 1996-1998 || Joined [[OJHL|OPJHL]]\n|- align=\"center\"\n| '''[[Scarborough Sabres]]''' || [[Scarborough, Toronto|Scarborough]] || 1970-1972 || Folded\n|- align=\"center\"\n| '''[[Scarborough Young Bruins]]''' || [[Scarborough, Toronto|Scarborough]] || 1976-1979 || Folded\n|- align=\"center\"\n| '''[[St. Michael's Buzzers]]''' || [[Toronto]] || 1956-1995 || Joined [[OJHL|OPJHL]]\n|- align=\"center\"\n| '''[[Shelburne Wolves]]''' || [[Shelburne, Ontario|Shelburne]] || 1995-1998 || Joined [[OJHL|OPJHL]]\n|- align=\"center\"\n| '''[[Syracuse Stars Jr. A|Syracuse Jr. Crunch]]''' || [[Syracuse, New York|Syracuse]] || 1995-1998 || Joined [[OJHL|OPJHL]]\n|- align=\"center\"\n| '''[[Thornhill Rattlers]]''' || [[Thornhill, Ontario|Thornhill]] || 1989-1998 || Joined [[OJHL|OPJHL]]\n|- align=\"center\"\n| '''[[Toronto Nationals (1970\u201